%h2
  Timestamp:
  =Time.now.strftime('%s')

%p
  Below is a simple scaffold as generated by Mizugumo's scaffold generator.  It
  exhibits AJAX behavior and degrades gracefully both the AJAX requests and the
  'delete' links, which normally require JavaScript in Rails.

%p
  Turn off JavaScript in your browser to see the gracefully-degraded behavior.

%hr

%h1 List of products

#products
  %table.scaffold
    %tr
      %th Name
      %th Description
      %th Price
      %th{:colspan => 3}
    =render @products

  = link_to 'New Product', new_product_path, :class => 'new_product'

